subject: Your GitLens Pro Trial is ending!
body: Hey there,Today is the last day of your GitLens Pro trial. To continue using the powerful GitLens+ features like the Commit Graph, richer integration with GitLab Self-Managed, Worktrees and Visual File History with your private repos, upgrade to a paid GitLens plan. If you don't need access to GitLens+ features with private repos, no action is needed! You can continue to use these features for free with public repos forever.
